{"tid":1044504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警大埔駕電單車撞欄 送院不治 長腿女途人相救","createTime":"2019-03-03T03:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T03:17:37.000Z","uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"602cfe6e27844118d1b3d2424fbf637e0ecf2b1f","tid":1044504,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"大埔太和路支路發生致命車禍，昨晚約11時42分，一名33歲男子，駕駛本田CB1000R大馬力電單車，沿太和路往吐露港公路上水方向行駛，其間在一個上斜右彎失控，「波勾」撞向左邊鐵欄，電單車衝前10多米才停下，司機拋出車外，頭部重創昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，死者是一名休班警員，事發時有其他駕駛人士經過，見狀立即停車報警及協助救援。救護員到場將傷者送大埔那打素醫院搶救，惜延至零時28分不治。警方將出事電單車拖返大欖涌車輛檢驗中心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190303/59323955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59323955&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=ab0f2656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190303%2F59323955&h=bbc4053d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190303/59323955</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190303/large/1551575546_9e61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190303%2Flarge%2F1551575546_9e61.jpg&h=9e59cd19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip"},{"pid":"34f7452b2b15bfaa5e01c1c5d1bd53b376e211bc","tid":1044504,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"條腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}